00:08:18.639 --> 00:08:19.240
I did.

00:08:20.439 --> 00:08:21.680
That's alright.

00:08:22.079 --> 00:08:23.040
Give me the Lion Seal

00:08:23.319 --> 00:08:24.720
and I'll let you have this.

00:08:24.800 --> 00:08:25.079
Hey.

00:08:25.639 --> 00:08:26.720
Why are you

00:08:26.879 --> 00:08:28.319
coveting our valuable?

00:08:29.959 --> 00:08:31.959
No one despises money.

00:08:32.399 --> 00:08:33.399
It's a shame that you're stupid.

00:08:36.310 --> 00:08:36.519
Don't...

