00:09:22.320 --> 00:09:23.360
Get me a gun.

00:09:24.720 --> 00:09:25.559
Don't try anything funny.

00:09:31.639 --> 00:09:33.240
Be it the Ruan family

00:09:33.519 --> 00:09:34.759
or the Huofeng Gang,

00:09:34.759 --> 00:09:35.919
I must get back at him!

00:09:36.639 --> 00:09:38.679
Otherwise, what's the point
of pretending to be Huo Qingwan?

00:09:39.799 --> 00:09:40.320
Qingwan...

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:43.440
Give me a gun.

