I'll teach you
how to become Huo Qingwan.

00:10:47.360 --> 00:10:49.039
You should teach me how to kill.

00:10:50.799 --> 00:10:51.919
When you become Huo Qingwan,

00:10:52.720 --> 00:10:55.120
I will always be your gun.

